Package org.rcsb.mbt.structLoader

This package provides classes which enable molecular biology data sets (such as protein structures, sequence data, etc) to be loaded into an MBT application as a Structure object.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IBatchStructureLoader Defines the standard interface for classes which know how to load Structure objects.
IFileStructureLoader Defines the standard interface for classes which know how to load a Structure from a file or url object.
IStructureLoader Defines the standard interface for classes which know how to load Structure objects.
IStructureXMLHandler Temporary refactor to allow applications to construct app-specific versions of the structure XML handler.
 

Class Summary
CifStructureLoader Implements the StructureLoader interface to enable reading of Cif files either from local disk or from a URL.
FastaStructureLoader Implements the StructureLoader interface to enable reading of Fasta files either from local disk or from a URL.
PdbStructureLoader Implements the StructureLoader interface to enable reading of PDB files either from local disk or from a URL.
RcsbStructureLoader Implements a BatchStructureLoader that uses the CifStructureLoader to laod mmCIF data from the RCSB ftp archive site.
StructureFactory Provides a central StructureLoader registry and Structure object factory.
StructureXMLHandler Invoked by the SAX while parsing the XML file.
TestStructureLoader Implements the StructureLoader interface to provide randomly generated PDB data for testing purposes.
 

Enum Summary
StructureXMLHandler.eIsParsing Parsing flags - some of the end element operations are controlled by these
 

Package org.rcsb.mbt.structLoader Description

This package provides classes which enable molecular biology data sets (such as protein structures, sequence data, etc) to be loaded into an MBT application as a Structure object. For example, the "getBatchStructure" method of the org.rcsb.mbt.structureLoader.StructureFactory class could be called in order to request that the default BatchStructureLoader implementation should load a specified data set.
